{"tid":1485774,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[福建獨立]美國聯邦快遞承運到內地包裹藏槍　內地警方立案調查","createTime":"2019-08-18T16:38:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T04:48:51.000Z","uid":104684,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a78e9c2c2df82d16bb4afba3084e86319b947e21","tid":1485774,"uid":104684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:38:56.000Z","msg":"美國聯邦快遞一個寄往福建的包裹藏有槍支，內地警方展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n福建福州市公安局表示，當地一間運動用品公司收到一個由美國客戶寄出的聯邦快遞包裹，當中藏有一支槍，福州警方已經扣起這支槍，並立案調查。 <br />\n<br />\n央視評論說，聯邦快遞早前已經將中國電訊設備商華為的快件轉至美國，強調中國已建立「不可靠實體清單」制度，如果聯邦快遞要搶著飲頭啖湯，可以幫忙。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>支持福建獨立</strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">福建幫誓殺習近平，血洗中南海，光復中華</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1475382-20190818.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1475382-20190818.htm&d=T%2BmtXVGNOTzTHFJD9Tq3caDCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=654df0eb\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1475382-20190818.htm&h=de993509\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1475382-20190818.htm</a>"},{"pid":"4c9db1b55883f4e36589d48dc0072309ca1cc809","tid":1485774,"uid":275634,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:40:56.000Z","msg":"支持福獨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d9191f019f3dfe83c4cd236ffc9522ff33e990a2","tid":1485774,"uid":62321,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:54:38.000Z","msg":"福建獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"209bfaf1831709bbe51e6e2625e4b506fdf39ba1","tid":1485774,"uid":44458,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T17:04:49.000Z","msg":"支持福建血洗中南海，光復中華"},{"pid":"d1b1f0a2a1853a7a88680256bf167a406e26b971","tid":1485774,"uid":104684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T04:48:51.000Z","msg":"福建獨立<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />光復中華<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}